projectGridLines.title: Gen AI Engineer Internship
projectGridLines.description:
Description: As part of our ongoing efforts to revamp our products with cutting-edge

Gen AI solutions, we are seeking talented individuals who are eager to gain hands-on

experience.

At iamneo, interns will be exposed to real-time challenges, providing them with

invaluable professional experience. This is a fantastic opportunity for students to

work on projects that significantly impact the education technology sector.

Skill sets: Full stack dev

Traits expectation: Analytical thinking

Expected learning: AI Engineering
